<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language>英文</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Thu, 01 Jun 2023 19:48:46 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Vimeo will stop supporting its TV apps on June 27th]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>众所周知，Vimeo <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-10-30-vimeo-linkedin-publishing.html">回避挑战 YouTube</a>而转而充当对企业友好的视频平台，现在这正在影响其客厅应用程序。该公司将于 6 月 27 日<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://help.vimeo.com/hc/en-us/articles/12425990752529--Learn-more-about-Vimeo-ending-support-for-TV-apps#:~:text=Important%20update%20regarding%20support%20for,for%20our%20existing%20TV%20apps">终止</a>对其当前电视应用程序的支持，包括 Android TV、Apple TV、Fire TV 和 Roku 设备的版本。它们将不再在应用商店中提供，您也不会看到任何更新。如果您想在大屏幕上观看剪辑，您必须使用 Apple AirPlay 或 Google Cast 从移动设备流式传输它。我们已向 Vimeo 征求意见。</p><p>该公司对其推理相当清楚。对创意和公司的关注意味着那些电视应用程序不是优先事项，Vimeo 上架的产品“不再符合[其]标准”。换句话说，Vimeo 不会维护不符合其战略并且会越来越落后的应用程序。该公司声称，铸造将提供“更好的持续体验”。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="72ae7f688b87443190b34bd54b74c432"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">亲爱的<a href="https://twitter.com/Vimeo?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Vimeo</a> 。我用你的应用程序来做一切。这是否意味着我无法在电视上观看“稍后观看”列表中保存的数百个视频中的任何一个？来吧...... <a href="https://t.co/QsXw7VrKta">pic.twitter.com/QsXw7VrKta</a></p> - Ted Geoghegan (@tedgeoghegan) <a href="https://twitter.com/tedgeoghegan/status/1661874735129436161?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 25 日</a></blockquote></div><p>当然，要注意的是，您可能<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/tedgeoghegan/status/1661874735129436161">仍会使用</a>Vimeo 来观看自己喜欢的视频。从客厅浏览“稍后观看”队列的方法并不简单。虽然这不会阻止您在电视上观看视频，但这可能会使马拉松式的观看过程变得更加麻烦。不管喜欢与否，Vimeo 很乐意将您引导至您的计算机或手机以进行任何扩展流式传输。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/vimeo-will-stop-supporting-its-tv-apps-on-june-27th-194846561.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/vimeo-will-stop-supporting-its-tv-apps-on-june-27th-194846561.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 75d9b0ef-0f8a-4c71-b746-a10ddbe9626d</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 01 Jun 2023 19:48:46 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685648927</ingested><modified> 2023-06-01T19:48:50+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/988bc3b0-00ae-11ee-bfdb-fb13b9239b16" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/988bc3b0-00ae-11ee-bfdb-fb13b9239b16" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Focal Foto/Flickr]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Vimeo app on iPhone]]></